True, but ISP's of over 360 sec have been achived with LOX/Kerosene.  I was using a value of 340 for my calculations.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>5. In chemical rocketry using lower specific impulse fuels<br>
requires more required lift off weight on the launch pad.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
